      "scaleFrom": 1.0,
      "scaleTo": 1.06,
      "_speech": "Most people have no idea football boots are being flipped for profit every single week.",
      "image": "topics/reel-001/boot-closeup.jpg"
    },
    {
      "startSec": 4.2,
      "endSec": 8.5,
      "objectPosition": "center center",
      "scaleFrom": 1.0,
      "scaleTo": 1.08,
      "_speech": "Here's how it actually works. Someone buys a limited Adidas Predator Elite at retail",
      "image": "topics/reel-001/predator-boot.jpg"
    },
    {
      "startSec": 8.5,
      "endSec": 13.0,
      "objectPosition": "center center",
      "scaleFrom": 1.0,
      "scaleTo": 1.05,
      "_speech": "let's say \u00c2\u00a3200. Two weeks later, it's listed on StockX for \u00c2\u00a3310. After fees, that's a clean \u00c2\u00a380 profit in 14 days.",
      "image": "topics/reel-001/cash-profit.jpg"
    },
    {
      "startSec": 13.0,
      "endSec": 17.5,
      "objectPosition": "center center",
      "scaleFrom": 1.0,
      "scaleTo": 1.08,
      "_speech": "The reason it works is simple: Nike, Adidas, and Mizuno release limited colourways",
      "image": "topics/reel-001/limited-boot.jpg"
    },
    {
      "startSec": 17.5,
      "endSec": 21.0,
      "objectPosition": "center center",
      "scaleFrom": 1.0,
      "scaleTo": 1.06,
      "_speech": "in batches of under 500 pairs. They sell out in under 20 minutes.",
      "image": "topics/reel-001/boot-shelf.jpg"
    },
    {
      "startSec": 21.0,
      "endSec": 25.5,
      "objectPosition": "center 60%",
      "scaleFrom": 1.0,
      "scaleTo": 1.08,
      "_speech": "Demand stays high. Supply doesn't come back.",
      "image": "topics/reel-001/player-feet.jpg"
    },
    {
      "startSec": 25.5,
      "endSec": 30.0,
      "objectPosition": "center center",
      "scaleFrom": 1.0,
      "scaleTo": 1.06,
      "_speech": "That gap is where the profit lives.",
      "image": "topics/reel-001/money-stack.jpg"
    },
    {
      "startSec": 30.0,
      "endSec": 34.5,
      "objectPosition": "center center",
      "scaleFrom": 1.0,
      "scaleTo": 1.08,
      "_speech": "And right now the market is moving fast \u00e2\u20ac\u201d boots we tracked this week are already up 25 to 40 percent.",
      "image": "topics/reel-001/mercurial-boot.jpg"
    },
    {
      "startSec": 34.5,
      "endSec": 38.5,
